AGI -&nbsp; Several people were wounded in a shooting at the court of the German city of Bielefield, in North Rhine-Westphalia. Bild told us. According to the newspaper, an attacker barricaded himself in the court.&nbsp; eyewitnesses report that several people are on the ground wounded,» explains Wdr.
In the court, a trial hearing was held against the alleged murder of the German boxer Besar Nimani, killed by gunshots at Bielefeld on 9 March 2024 while leaving a store.&nbsp; Among the wounded would be the father and brother of the defendant in the proceedings. &nbsp;
"We do part of a wider police operation in the city center, in Niederwall. Avoid the area around the Niederwall" is what we read in the social profiles of the Police.

